OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy today with a few
OL,6,Fbrighter spells at times. Showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain will spread across
OL,8,FCumbria through the day. Feeling hot
OL,9,Fand humid, particularly in the
OL,10,Fsunshine in the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FHeavy rain may develop this
OL,13,Fevening with a risk of thunderstorms.
OL,14,FRain gradually easing in the early
OL,15,Fhours. A warm and muggy night with
OL,16,Ftemperatures in the high-teens.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FDry and sunny on Tuesday with
OL,19,Fblue skies and strong sunshine. Very
OL,20,Fhot and humid, particularly in
OL,21,Fsouthern parts of the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
