OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying very hot, with extreme heat at
OL,7,Ftimes in the south. High humidity will
OL,8,Fbring very warm, muggy nights. Largely
OL,9,Fdry and sunny, but increasingly cloudy
OL,10,Fwith showers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
